Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.90,0:00:15.30,Defaul,,0000,0000,0000,,翻译:basaka[dmhy]，校对:kire[popgo]、SORA[popgo]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯  速瀨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.78,0:00:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狀態不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.36,0:00:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了這個感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.93,0:00:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個成績的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.97,0:00:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  這麼心神不寧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.50,0:00:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.54,0:00:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7分  5分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.93,0:00:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6分  4分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.14,0:00:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3分  5分  7分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.04,0:00:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總計37分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離合格還差得很遠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.37,0:01:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你突然冒出來算什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,37分又是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.11,0:01:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  孝之君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.02,0:01:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.12,0:01:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...難道說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...我妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是涼宮茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.86,0:01:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照  鳴海孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道今天她也和我們一起？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.30,0:01:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她只是跟來...而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.57,0:01:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是暑假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.50,0:01:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不會閑到來打擾兩位火熱的約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.33,0:01:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火熱...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.58,0:01:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去泳池了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.27,0:01:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還不能“吃了”姐姐哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.05,0:01:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  臉紅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.90,0:01:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是純情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.53,0:01:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...這...這個臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  孝之君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜又說了什麼奇怪的話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.79,0:02:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜一直這麼活蹦亂跳的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.97,0:02:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...有點過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.95,0:02:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.02,0:02:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜的腔調有點像速瀨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...茜也是游泳部的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.38,0:02:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還參加過大會得過獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是以水月為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪  前途險惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚沒睡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在玩慎二借給我的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果就早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這樣對身體不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.13,0:02:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學習上怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬虎虎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之君也考白陵大多好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.40,0:03:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,港陽大太遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白陵大的話又近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又能一起上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.75,0:03:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始努力的話  一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以孝之君也考白陵大...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時叫醒我就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.10,0:03:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是孝之君睡得很香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.93,0:03:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表情很可愛  就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.51,0:03:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.17,0:03:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.23,0:03:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我帶來了好東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方坐下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  沒有碎掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦~~  肉餡餅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.83,0:04:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我聽說孝之君喜歡吃肉餡餅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  其實很早以前就開始試著做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直做不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的也有點不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃的話就直說  不要勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.90,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也吃吃看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  這次做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的  所以今天...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話  上來坐坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.71,0:05:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會覺得不自在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...沒有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.51,0:05:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼  快點上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來還是不進來  哪個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3，2，1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.06,0:06:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.60,0:06:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...已經是晚上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然來打擾未免太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.60,0:06:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在意那種事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等...等等  茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了  帶客人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.38,0:06:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海君  不用這麼緊張啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來  不要客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不夠的話儘管說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再為你做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜  你玩夠沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  孝之君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.50,0:07:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了  茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛在想 H 的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個...真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.77,0:07:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...倒不是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.49,0:07:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想有個哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來有點靠不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.44,0:07:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就湊合著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.07,0:07:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  哥哥你一定要和姐姐結婚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜  你在說什麼啊  真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了  將來的事先不說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:08:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交往的時候可要好好對待遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天的夏祭沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.02,0:08:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  父母同意延長門限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是水月說有事不能來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.71,0:08:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是交了男朋友了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.78,0:08:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎  原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.71,0:08:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.64,0:08:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月說她有男朋友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不能來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜說在街上看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她和一個男人走在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天就我們兩個去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去管他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對待平君不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.52,0:08:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是鳴海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事的話請聽到提示音後留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速瀨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天為什麼不接電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你重新打過來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.92,0:09:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我不在的時候你打了3次來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聽我說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.03,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有關男朋友的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有男朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在一起而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是昨天他向我表白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那交往嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.64,0:10:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得該怎麼辦好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你問我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己的選擇的話我會支持你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說雖然不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.28,0:10:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第10個向我表白的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是都被我甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這算是在自誇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  小心我扁你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都稱讚我的頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻很討厭它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.38,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這頭長髮代表了那個討厭的固執的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今沒有稱讚過它的只有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.09,0:11:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說還是短髮適合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...對那個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事我自己也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定了  這次也不交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.48,0:11:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想像遙一樣正視自己的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  這樣也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏祭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  你和遙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  過會兒去道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二  遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之  你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明說今天兩個人去看夏祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把涼宮一個人扔在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還擔心你不來了一直在哭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了  平君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你們約好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我想找他談心拉他來這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近出了點事  所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然覺得對不起遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是水月的事也不能不管吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣  沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為水月是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.04,0:12:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.44,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家最終還是聚在這裏了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友夥伴就是這樣的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  難得大家都在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去看夏祭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就算謝罪我來請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前先一起拍一張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4個人一起拍照還是第一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.95,0:13:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以留作紀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再靠過來一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.10,0:13:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月很煩惱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.13,0:13:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我也會這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.45,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以孝之君能這麼關心水月  我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他們出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.71,0:14:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜也一起去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上來坐一會兒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想和你再聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是遙的房間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.50,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不好意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼盯著看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.91,0:14:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多連環畫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.00,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.85,0:14:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時的連環畫《瑪雅烏爾的禮物》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本書沒有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.85,0:14:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次兩個人一起去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想是將來成為連環畫作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以上了大學想專攻兒童心理學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.39,0:15:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會實現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.22,0:15:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候把我們4人的故事寫進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.34,0:15:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們回來了啊  真晚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你把姐姐“吃”了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.14,0:16:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是要妨礙我還是支持我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.98,0:17:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要著急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.38,0:17:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有的是時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.20,0:17:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之君  我們來念咒語吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.10,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣重複我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.05,0:17:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同無限夜空中的閃爍群星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.96,0:17:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的心交織在一起不分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.12,0:17:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使兩人無法牽手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們依然牢記……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之君也考白陵大多好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.11,0:18:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要考白陵大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.88,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在說要考  你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是樂觀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.78,0:18:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.15,0:18:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.71,0:18:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙要生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.04,0:18:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...有了這個就會原諒我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裏幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速瀨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這身打扮算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.01,0:19:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  參觀職業隊啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.17,0:19:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這口氣什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢  和遙約會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在柊町站前碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們相處得不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人羡慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好說好說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.56,0:19:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之  那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.74,0:19:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實今天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.16,0:19:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒指嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.68,0:19:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日禮物要戒指...你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對  對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.61,0:19:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎  但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.35,0:20:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送你不想要的東西你也不會高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大出血...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之  謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好珍惜它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.21,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我的生日時我要你10倍奉還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.01,0:20:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.71,0:20:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交通事故嗎  真危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.55,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙...會不會生氣回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個女孩子吧  好慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.49,0:21:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被車撞倒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.85,0:21:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在等人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.11,0:21:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.24,0:21:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.28,0:21:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.85,0:21:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.42,0:21:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓讓...對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.91,0:21:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.28,0:21:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪兒  遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.05,0:21:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本日14點15分發生事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.19,0:21:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從遺留的學生證照片確認是本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者姓名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.44,0:22:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白陵大附屬柊學園  3年級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.57,0:22:33.51,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,站在溫柔的微風中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.57,0:22:33.51,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,やわらかな風に抱かれ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.59,0:22:41.96,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,思念著你使我心痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.59,0:22:41.96,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,あなた想う心　切なくなる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.66,0:22:48.01,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人站在山丘上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.66,0:22:48.01,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,丘のうえひとりきりで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.74,0:22:55.17,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,目送著季節的逝去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.74,0:22:55.17,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,季節見送っているの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.59,0:23:02.61,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,遙望青空的彼岸可以看見什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.59,0:23:02.61,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,青空の向こう  何がみえるのかな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.15,0:23:10.28,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,心中默默祈禱“請賜予我勇氣”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.15,0:23:10.28,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,「勇気が欲しい」  静かに祈っている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.35,0:23:15.65,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,一去不复返了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.35,0:23:15.65,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,もう戻れない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.65,0:23:24.18,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,那依偎在你怀中的溫馨的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.65,0:23:24.18,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの腕に包まれていた優しい日々
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.18,0:23:35.08,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,單單殘留著夏日回憶的小小焰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.18,0:23:35.08,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,夏の記憶かすかに残ってる小さな花火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.08,0:23:42.32,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍然不熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.08,0:23:42.32,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,消えない  今でも
